[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[div style="text-align: center !important"]]
//[...]//
[[/div]]

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] Well?

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] I... I don't... I can't do this myself. You've shown me that. I need your help. You can't give up.

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] I'm only giving up what's already wasted. As soon as I'm back on my feet, I'll be back in the trenches. But we're going to be doing it right, this time. A proper, complete solution. No miracle cures.

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] Okay.

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] Okay?

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] Okay. Yes. This time will be different.

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] This time is the last time. I can't fight you again, Dougall. You're... you're all that's left of him.

= //<Silence on recording.>//

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] I don't want to hate either of you anymore.
[[/div]]
