> You have (1) new messages.

[[div class="blockquote mcd sms"]]

> [[span class="ir"]]R:[[/span]] They did find him, you know, after a fashion. It took her a month to reverse-engineer and then adapt the old DePLExA referent seeker to pick up his Daumal signature, altered state or no, but she did it. 
> 
> He's still out there.

[[div class="table6"]]
> [[span class="mcd"]]P:[[/span]] I'm busy. Is there something you want?
[[/div]]

> [[span class="ir"]]R:[[/span]] He was blundering aimlessly around in some ideospheric trash heap, in between darting in and out of time and space, looking for... well, you know what he was looking for. And you know what he's unleashed already in the process, not that you care.

[[div class="table6"]]
> [[span class="mcd"]]P:[[/span]] You might be surprised.
[[/div]]

> [[span class="ir"]]R:[[/span]] I'm sending you the snapshot she took; I hope you take a good, long look.

[[div class="table6"]]
> [[span class="mcd"]]P:[[/span]] What response are you looking for here? Regret? Satisfaction? 
> 
> You know how it goes, Ilse.
[[/div]]

> [[span class="ir"]]R:[[/span]] You left her holding the bag. Both of you. I want you to acknowledge that.

[[div class="table6"]]
> [[span class="mcd"]]P:[[/span]] I've got nothing to give you. Not until this is done.
[[/div]]

> [[span class="ir"]]R:[[/span]] But it never will be DONE, will it?

[[div class="table6"]]
> [[span class="mcd"]]P:[[/span]] You KNOW how it goes.

> [[span class="mcd"]]P:[[/span]] You play your part, and I'll play mine.
[[/div]]

[[/div]]

